dc_title_s: Congressional Districts: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2012
dc_description_s: This coverage represents the boundaries of the congressional districts partially or entirely within Prince George's County. While this coverage is maintained by the Prince George's County GIS Section, the boundaries are defined and its representation approved by the Board of Elections. This layer was last updated in January 23, 2012 and compiled at 1:2,400.
